claim.claim-text:
A car (1) comprising:
a frame (2), which supports a pair of front wheels (3) and a pair of rear wheels (5);
a passenger compartment (7), which is arranged between the front wheels (3) and the rear wheels (5);
at least one pair of doors (8), which are hinged to the frame (2) and allow access into the passenger compartment (7); and
an underbody (11), which delimits the car (1) on the lower side, faces the road surface, and comprises an aerodynamic diffuser (12), which is arranged in a rear position and comprises a chute (13) presenting a height with respect to the road surface that progressively increases when longitudinally moving from the front to the rear;
wherein the underbody (11) comprises a pair of aerodynamic channels (14), each of which extends longitudinally, leads to the aerodynamic diffuser (12), is open on the lower side towards the road surface, and presents, in its transverse section, an area that progressively increases when longitudinally moving from the front to the rear;
the car (1) is characterized in that each aerodynamic channel (14) has a segment which is arranged under a corresponding door (8).
